            <commentid>14278</commentid>
            <who name="Ivan Furnadjiev">ivan</who>
            <bug_when>2009-11-23 10:20:11 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>Using the qx.client.History class leads to empty page if the application is loaded in IFrame. In IE this leads to &quot;access denied error&quot;. The reason for this issue is &quot;top.location.href&quot; and &quot;top.location.hash&quot; used in qx.client.History. The fix is to use &quot;window.location.href&quot; and &quot;window.location.hash&quot; instead.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
